---
import LegalLayout from "../layouts/LegalLayout.astro";
---

<LegalLayout title="Privacy Policy" noindex={true}>
  <section class="max-w-3xl section-wrap py-12 sm:py-16">
    <h1 class="heading-hero text-3xl">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 text-base body-text">
      <div>
        <h2 class="heading-section text-xl mb-2">1. Overview</h2>
        <p>
          This privacy policy informs you about the type, scope, and purpose of
          the processing of personal data on this website. The responsible party
          for data processing on this website is Martina Mustermann, Berlin,
          Germany.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="heading-section text-xl mb-2">
          2. Data Collection on This Website
        </h2>
        <p>
          This is a static website. We do not collect, process, or store
          personal data through server-side technologies such as cookies,
          tracking pixels, or analytics tools.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="heading-section text-xl mb-2">3. Newsletter</h2>
        <p>
          If you subscribe to our newsletter via the MailerLite form widget,
          your email address will be processed by MailerLite under their privacy
          policy. We use MailerLite solely to send release alerts and updates.
          You can unsubscribe at any time.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="heading-section text-xl mb-2">4. External Links</h2>
        <p>
          This website contains links to external websites (e.g., Amazon, social
          media platforms). We have no influence on the content and data
          processing of these third-party sites. Opening these links is your
          choice and not initiated by this website.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="heading-section text-xl mb-2">5. Theme Preference</h2>
        <p>
          The theme toggle on this website stores your display preference (dark,
          light, or high-contrast) in your browser's local storage. This data is
          stored exclusively on your device and is not transmitted to or
          accessible by us.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="heading-section text-xl mb-2">6. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>
          You have the right to information, correction, deletion, restriction
          of processing, data portability, and objection regarding your personal
          data. To exercise these rights, contact
          hello[at]martinamustermann.com.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 text-xs text-text-tertiary">
      <p>Last updated: April 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</LegalLayout>
